[The fusion reaches its peak:]
chant syllables] (‚ÄúGlo‚Äîri‚Äîa‚Äù) [chopped and looped into polyrhythms,]
[synth pads swell like digital choirs,
the beat glitches, breaks, and reforms.

[Outro]
[The chant echoes once more:]
‚ÄúGloria in excelsis Deo‚Ä¶‚Äù
